and RIP Frank Zappa

I've only ever had this @ 256k mp3 - the best I could find. (Couldn't even afford the second-hand copies on eBay.) If I can get hold of this in lossless, I'll be grateful to you for, like, eternity...

I can confirm this is the goods - and thanks for the fast upload!  I'll keep this shared for a good few weeks.  A lot of Zappa fans will bless you for this one, lonesomecowboy. (Or can I call you Burt for short?)
